snippet: Roger Federer is seeded No. 7 for the United States Open, his first slot outside the top three in singles at a Grand Slam tournament since he was 13th at Flushing Meadows in 2002.
abstract: Roger Federer is seeded seventh at the United States Open, his first slot outside the top three in singles at a Grand Slam tennis tournament since 2002; other tennis news noted.
